spec_data.Name: python3-django-compressor
spec_data.Description:
Django Compressor combines and compresses linked and inline Javascript
or CSS in a Django templates into cacheable static files by using the
``compress`` template tag.  HTML in between
``{% compress js/css %}`` and ``{% endcompress %}`` is
parsed and searched for CSS or JS. These styles and scripts are subsequently
processed with optional, configurable compilers and filters.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 12:31:50 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Compresses linked and inline JavaScript or CSS into single cached files
